  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Coronavirus: How to help safely
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Across the UK people are playing their part and providing essential support to their friends and family who are in isolation.</p>

  </div>
</div>

